        "2. **Impressions (From Explore, Hashtags, Other):** While total impressions can be inflated, breaking them down by source is incredibly insightful. High impressions from the Explore page and hashtags indicate strong algorithmic favor and effective **hashtag strategy Instagram** and **Instagram explore page algorithm** optimization.",
